# model

**Instance Property**

The model of the vehicle.

## Declaration

```swift
var model: String? { get set }
```

## Discussion

Examples might include “Civic” or “Escape”.

## Specifying the Vehicle Description

- **registrationPlate**: The text on the license plate or registration plate of the vehicle.
- **manufacturer**: The name of the vehicle’s manufacturer.
